title: Student Athlete of the Week: Darby Welsh
text:
Previous Next 
She was five when she started doing headers and six when she did the buddy pass for the first time. 
Now, Darby Welsh is a superstar sophomore at St. Paul's School for Girls. She has another trophy to add to her book shelf, Darby is the Gardiner Wolf Furniture Student Athlete of the Week. 
Watch the video above to see why Darby is our Gardiner Wolf Furniture Student Athlete of the Week.
